des:
Control your AFTO smart devices by voice command. The AFTO smart devices are including smart bulb, socket, plug, IR, camera, etc

After connecting Alexa to your AFTO products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our " AFTO" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one AFTO account in our " AFTO" app;
(3). You need to have some AFTO devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " AFTO" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "AFTO" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "AFTO" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "AFTO", and you'll be navigated to AFTO login page;
(9). Input your AFTO account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

Example command:
- Alexa, turn on living room light
- Alexa, turn off living room light
- Alexa, set the bedroom lights to 50%
- Alexa set the bedroom lights to blue
- Alexa, turn on the bedroom air conditioner
- Alexa, turn off the TV
